text: Novomukatovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Ryazanovsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 6 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Sterlitamak, 7 km from Ryazanovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Novomukatovka
